# SMR99 Nexus Whitepaper

## Introduction
SMR99 Nexus is an AI-powered reward and reputation protocol built on BNB Chain.

## Problem
Fake engagement and bots dominate many crypto communities.

## Solution
A system that rewards real users using AI and blockchain verification.

## Technology
- AI analysis  
- Blockchain transparency  
- Smart contract rewards  

## Token Utility
SMR99 is used for rewards, staking, governance, and premium features.

## Vision
A fair and transparent Web3 ecosystem.

## Conclusion
SMR99 Nexus aims to redefine how communities interact in crypto
